data.description: Location, Location, Did I say Location?! Lovely updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath home for sale. Home location is 208 Velma Drive, Wellston, Oh 45692. Located in a very nice subdivision, which is semi secluded. Which gives you a country feel. The house offers an eat in kitchen/dining room, which is great for entertaining your loved ones and guest. The kitchen island has built in sink, no more looking at the wall. All the bedrooms are good sized. The master bedroom offers a master bath with separate shower and large tub. The property also offers mature trees and plenty of off street parking. The home has fresh paint, flooring, window treatments, new deck. The owners are throwing in enough flooring to finish the living room for the buyer. The home offers nearly 1 acre for your enjoyment. You are also very close to Lake Alma for hours of family fun enjoyment. Additional parcels: M240040201100, M240040201200
